---
/**
 * Hero component for blog homepage
 * Fully static, zero JS, LCP-friendly
 */
---

<section class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pt-16 pb-10">
  <blockquote class="space-y-10 text-center">
    <p
      class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl"
    >
      “A reader lives a thousand lives before he dies.
      The man who never reads lives only one.”
    </p>

    <footer class="text-sm tracking-wide text-muted-foreground">
      — George R. R. Martin
    </footer>
  </blockquote>

</section>
